     Each person posting a petition had played a certain amount of classes past a certain level. Say 3 different classes past level 30 to 40's, or possibly multiple high level classes, since we are wanting to change the high end game for druids.  I see this as a better solution that would be more valuable to VI.  I know this would be more difficult to put together but I think we have a lot of good ideas that could be revised and sent out by qualified people.<br>
     What I was thinking was to have some sort of outline which could easily guide each individual to compare and contrast within each class that they have played at the high end game.  Even if we had 20% of the respondents of the previous post, this would be a more viable way to get our point across to VI.  <br>
     Wondering if there is any support out there to help get this put together.  Remember persistence pays off in the end..<br>
<br>
