Just one question: How do your solo abilities make you a better group player? The memmed spell layout is TOTALLY different. I'm not showing a 'holier-than-thou' attitude, I'm addressing an issue, and if you felt included in my description about people creating Druid Alts to farm dungeons, well, just ask yourself whether you're one of them.<br>
I'm sick of getting $hit because there are so many bad players around due to the nature of a Druid's skill allowing for this. Do NOT get the issues mixed up.<br>
I'm a very humble player, I'm not trying to teach anyone anything they shouldn't already know, just shedding light on an old subject from a different perspective. Discuss the issue with valid arguments, don't attack me for showing you it.<br>
